Raov()ezANOVA()aov()

# 
library(tidyr)
library(ggplot2)

# 
set.seed(123)
data <- data.frame(
  Subject = factor(1:10),
  Time1 = rnorm(10, mean = 70, sd = 5),
  Time2 = rnorm(10, mean = 75, sd = 5),
  Time3 = rnorm(10, mean = 80, sd = 5)
)

# 
long_data <- gather(data, key = "Time", value = "Score", Time1, Time2, Time3)

# 
aov_result <- aov(Score ~ Time + Error(Subject/Time), data = long_data)
str(aov_result)
